videos.description: Mississippi State's K.J. Costello lets it soar deep to the end zone, but Texas A&M's Myles Jones gets in the way and picks off the Bulldogs.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Aggies’ Jones reaches back for a perfect INT) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aggies' Jones reaches back for a perfect INT

videos.description: The Aggies block Mississippi State's punt and they're able to capitalize on the turnover with a 1-yard Isaiah Spiller touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Blocked punt leads to Texas A&M touchdown) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Blocked punt leads to Texas A&M touchdown

videos.description: Kellen Mond's pass is intercepted by Emmanuel Forbes and returned for a 60-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mississippi State gets on the board with pick-6) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mississippi State gets on the board with pick-6

videos.description: Kellen Mond flips a short pass to Chase Lane who takes off running and hits pay dirt for a 51-yard touchdown vs. Mississippi State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Aggies respond to pick-6 with 51-yard touchdown) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Aggies respond to pick-6 with 51-yard touchdown

videos.description: Jayden Peevy recovers Mississippi State's fumble and returns it for a 19-yard gain. A couple of plays later, Ainias Smith walks in an easy six-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Mond, Aggies take advantage of Bulldogs’ fumble with TD) 2020/10/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mond, Aggies take advantage of Bulldogs' fumble with TD

videos.description: No. 11 Texas A&M head coach Jimbo Fisher commends the defense on its big turnover and blocked punt in a win against Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Fisher says Aggies' defense was outstanding

videos.description: The No. 11 Aggies running back Isaiah Spiller dominated the field rushing for 114 yards and 2 TDs in a 28-14 win over Mississippi State.
videos.headline: Texas A&M runs past State for second straight win
